The paper deals with problems related to dominating sets and edge dominating sets in graphs and hypergraphs, which are fundamental topics in graph theory and combinatorial optimization. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), followed by cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), cs.CG (Computational Geometry), cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
